00:01:22.480 --> 00:01:23.880
[Annette Lamothe-Ramos]: "Kingdom of the Little People"

00:01:23.880 --> 00:01:25.380
was founded in 2009

00:01:25.380 --> 00:01:26.840
by wealthy real-estate mogul,

00:01:26.840 --> 00:01:28.000
Chen Mingjing;

00:01:28.260 --> 00:01:29.460
and, as you can imagine,

00:01:29.460 --> 00:01:30.780
has since been the centre

00:01:30.780 --> 00:01:32.100
of a lot of controversy.

00:01:32.760 --> 00:01:33.900
Media outlets like

00:01:33.940 --> 00:01:34.880
the Daily Mail,

00:01:34.880 --> 00:01:35.900
The New York Times;

00:01:35.900 --> 00:01:37.140
and organizations like

00:01:37.140 --> 00:01:38.480
Little People of America

00:01:38.480 --> 00:01:40.280
and Handicap International

00:01:40.360 --> 00:01:41.560
have criticized the park

00:01:41.640 --> 00:01:44.440
with claims that it's the equivalent of a human zoo,

00:01:44.680 --> 00:01:47.500
