00:05:41.680 --> 00:05:42.780
[Annette Lamothe-Ramos]: Employees here

00:05:42.880 --> 00:05:45.300
mainly suffer from two forms of dwarfism:

00:05:45.720 --> 00:05:47.280
disproportionate dwarfism,

00:05:47.460 --> 00:05:49.480
the umbrella term for genetic disorders that

00:05:49.480 --> 00:05:52.000
cause unusual proportions of their body parts;

00:05:52.380 --> 00:05:54.040
and proportionate dwarfism,

00:05:54.220 --> 00:05:56.580
which results from hormonal deficiency.

00:05:56.620 --> 00:05:58.020
What they all have in common,

00:05:58.100 --> 00:05:59.240
is that they're no taller

00:05:59.240 --> 00:06:01.020
than 4 feet, 3 inches;

00:06:01.020 --> 00:06:02.320
